snippet.title: Fabled Lands Narrative RPG Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Fabled Lands is a challenging old-school narrative tactical RPG set in an open world. Complete quests, fight, trade goods and develop your character. Explore a vast land of adventure: travel across the war-torn kingdom, survive the plains of howling darkness, and escape the Court of Hidden Faces.

Add to your wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1299620/Fabled_Lands/

Official website: https://www.primegames.bg/en/blog/big-announcement
